{"tid":306897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你點睇？】穿熱褲坐捷運唔衞生？ 1張相引發網友熱議","createTime":"2017-07-03T02:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T02:19:27.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa39216e30c724b4057535e2b64c4936d8731fdb","tid":306897,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170702/large/1499011056_2d29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170702%2Flarge%2F1499011056_2d29.jpg&h=f97eba94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣炎熱，不少年輕女子都會穿超短熱褲外出，貪其涼快。可是，有台灣台北網民質疑，這些女子穿着這些露出大腿的熱褲坐捷運，皮膚直接接觸座椅，會不會很不衞生，他在網上公開一張在捷運上偷拍的照片，引來不少網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n可是，網民的重點不是衞生的問題，而是照片上留着短髮、穿著白色緊身上衣、超短牛仔熱褲，質疑：「你貼這個圖然後要我們討論衞生問題？」「重點不在腿吧&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n當然，亦有少部份網民是真的討論衞生問題，有網民說：「整個大腿肉都貼在椅子上，感覺就很不衞生！」「椅子不知道乾不乾淨，她穿這麼短直接貼上去可能會感染&hellip;&hellip;」「看來以後只能穿無塵衣坐捷運了！」"},{"pid":"0df85db02aca1d364b65b68012478162abeada68","tid":306897,"uid":9141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa560189a680e22133d879b114a45b89bad629f1","tid":306897,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"會令到架車有腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17efc2d5cdfaf25e22f5d03c30dd400a1b9c99a","tid":306897,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"好想瀨張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0370eb3460d285043ff1f52b92f86c8c5554afef","tid":306897,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmo